"{\"uid\": \"ejpress.org-belgium-foils-planned-terrorist-attack-on-eve-of-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Belgian authorities announced on Thursday a major anti-terrorist operation, which led to the arrest of seven suspects who, according to the Belgian Federal Prosecutor's Office are suspected of having prepared a \\\"terrorist attack\\\".\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.8956460512366277, \"rank\": 0.11651231089667995, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.8956460512366277, \"rank\": 0.11651231089667995, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Arnaud d'Oultremont, spokesman for the public prosecutor's office, fourteen searches were carried out across the country as part of this operation.\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The suspects arrested are due to appear before an anti-terrorism judge today, who will decide whether or not to keep them in custody.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Public Prosecutor's Office has specified that those arrested are suspected of \\\"participating in the activities of a terrorist group, financing terrorism and preparing a terrorist attack\\\".\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"score\": 0.9999985826101279, \"rank\": 1.417391971540351e-06, \"text\": \"Public Prosecutor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, details of potential targets or locations were not disclosed.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No link has been established at this stage with the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, whose opening ceremony will be held under tight security on Friday.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"European Jewish Press, Europe's sole Jewish news and information service.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9088684452266901, \"rank\": 0.07716275878735557, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}, {\"begin\": 982, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9088684452266901, \"rank\": 0.07716275878735557, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Launched end 2005, the European Jewish Press is the sole online Jewish news agency in Europe.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9088684452266901, \"rank\": 0.07716275878735557, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}, {\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jewish news agency\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The privately funded Brussels-based outlet is an independent media body.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It aims to provide both Jewish and non-Jewish audiences around the world with balanced, up-to-date and reliable news reports on issues of concern to the Jewish communities worldwide.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1211, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9088684452266901, \"rank\": 0.07716275878735557, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9088684452266901, \"rank\": 0.07716275878735557, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"European Jewish Press news are read by individuals, officials, experts, journalists and many others\\u2026.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9088684452266901, \"rank\": 0.07716275878735557, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"European Jewish Press is an affiliate of  Jewish News Syndicate (JNS) and collaborates with EU Reporter.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9088684452266901, \"rank\": 0.07716275878735557, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}, {\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_S._Tobin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jewish News Syndicate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http:/